request.description:
The API endpoint retrieves the details of a specific cart identified by the provided ID.

The response of the request can be documented as a JSON schema:

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "id": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "products": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "product": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "quantity": {
                        "type": "integer"
                    }
                },
                "required": ["product", "quantity"]
            }
        }
    },
    "required": ["id", "products"]
}

 ```
